.DT
steal
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
steal

.SH steal - Used to covertly take items off people
.SI 5
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
steal <object> from <living>
steal <object> from <container> in <living> 
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Steal is used to take items from another creature's inventory without
them noticing.

You cannot steal while in combat, however be prepared for hostile
response should you fail a steal.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> steal knife from igor
You steal the small knife from Igor.

> steal knife from igor
You tried to steal the small knife from Igor but were noticed.
Igor moves aggressively towards you!

> steal doll from backpack in igor
You tried to steal the wooden doll from Igor but were noticed.
Igor moves aggressively towards you!

> steal doll from backpack in igor
You steal the wooden doll from Igor.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
shoplift
.EP
